<?xml version='1.0' encoding='ISO-8859-1' ?>
<grammar>
<section>
<title>Suggestions and offers</title>
<sectiontitle>We use &lt;i&gt;Why don't we&lt;/i&gt; + verb and &lt;i&gt;How about &lt;/i&gt;+ verb + &lt;i&gt;-ing&lt;/i&gt; to make suggestions.</sectiontitle>
<titlesound>el_gram_12_2_1.mp3</titlesound>
<text1>I'm bored!</text1>
<text1a>&lt;b&gt;Why don't we go&lt;/b&gt; for a walk?</text1a>
<sound1>el_gram_12_2_2.mp3</sound1>
<text2></text2>
<text2a>&lt;b&gt;How about&lt;/b&gt; watch&lt;b&gt;ing&lt;/b&gt; a film?</text2a>
<sound2>el_gram_12_2_3.mp3</sound2>
<sectiontitle2>We also use &lt;i&gt;Let's&lt;/i&gt; + verb and &lt;i&gt;Shall I/we&lt;/i&gt; + verb.</sectiontitle2>
<titlesound2>el_gram_12_2_4.mp3</titlesound2>
<text3>What shall we do?</text3>
<text3a>&lt;b&gt;Let's stay&lt;/b&gt; at home.</text3a>
<sound3>el_gram_12_2_5.mp3</sound3>
<text4></text4>
<text4a>&lt;b&gt;Shall we listen&lt;/b&gt; to some music?</text4a>
<sound4>el_gram_12_2_6.mp3</sound4>
</section>
<section>
<title>Suggestions and offers</title>
<sectiontitle>We use &lt;i&gt;I'll&lt;/i&gt; + verb and &lt;i&gt;Shall I&lt;/i&gt; + verb to make offers.</sectiontitle>
<titlesound>el_gram_12_2_7.mp3</titlesound>
<text1>I can't open the window.</text1>
<text1a>&lt;b&gt;I'll help&lt;/b&gt; you.</text1a>
<sound1>el_gram_12_2_8.mp3</sound1>
<text2>This bag is very heavy.</text2>
<text2a>&lt;b&gt;Shall I carry&lt;/b&gt; it?</text2a>
<sound2>el_gram_12_2_9.mp3</sound2>
<sectiontitle2></sectiontitle2>
<titlesound2></titlesound2>
<text3></text3>
<text3a></text3a>
<sound3></sound3>
<text4></text4>
<text4a></text4a>
<sound4></sound4>
</section>
</grammar>